19
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:06,840
I don't drink beer.

20
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,280
I'll have juice.

21
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,080
I'll buy it.

22
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,280
Let me do it.

23
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,640
