49
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,520
Do you want to come?

50
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,840
You look pretty good.

51
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,760
How about I show you a good time?

52
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,240
