54
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,320
We can just leave them.

55
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:45,920
What do you mean?

56
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:46,920
Wait.

57
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:49,400
