59
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,200
Don't you understand what I mean?

60
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,120
Do you know who you're talking to?

61
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,520
Dong Shancai's boyfriend.

62
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,880
