80
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,440
He just hit me.

81
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:55,000
Keep your crazy boyfriend in check
instead of standing there.

82
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,400
That's enough.

83
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,600
