98
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,200
Xiaoyou's boyfriend.

99
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,280
Why should I?

100
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,000
Why did you hit him then?

101
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,480
I hit him

102
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,320
