237
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,320
No.

238
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:06,040
I think he's right.

239
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:08,320
The girl I saw today

240
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:10,080
